<li><strong>Internal Controls:</strong> Establish governance and compliance committees to oversee operations.</li>



<li><strong>Seeking Professional Guidance:</strong> Engage with legal and compliance consultants for expert advice.</li>



<li><strong>Continuous Monitoring:</strong> Stay updated and ensure ongoing compliance.</li>
</ol>



<p>By following these steps, you can tackle regulatory compliance challenges with sophistication.</p>
